<%= render 'shared/public_nav' %>

<div style="background: var(--bg);">

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" style="padding-top: 80px; padding-bottom: 80px;">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">
        Build the life you want,<br>one small habit at a time.
      </h1>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--ink-secondary); margin-top: 20px; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 500px;">
        Track your habits, manage tasks, set goals, and reflect daily — all in one calm, focused space. No points systems. No pushy notifications. Just a clear picture of who you're becoming.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top: 32px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <%= link_to new_user_registration_path, class: "v2-btn v2-btn-primary", style: "padding: 12px 28px; font-size: 0.933rem;" do %>
          Get started free
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to new_user_session_path, style: "font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.867rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); text-decoration: none;" do %>
          Already have an account? Sign in
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       WHAT YOU GET — feature grid
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 64px 0;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 12px;">One app for the whole picture.</h2>

      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.933rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 520px;">
        Most people use five apps to manage their day. Habit Beaver brings it together so nothing falls through the cracks.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <div class="v2-card" style="padding: 24px;">
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.03em; margin-bottom: 10px;">Habits</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.867rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-body); margin-bottom: 6px;">Know what to do every morning</div>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.833rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); line-height: 1.6;">
            Your dashboard groups today's habits by time of day. Morning routine, afternoon check-ins, evening wind-down — all laid out and ready to check off. Streaks and health scores show you where you're strong and where to refocus.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="v2-card" style="padding: 24px;">
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.03em; margin-bottom: 10px;">Tasks</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.867rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-body); margin-bottom: 6px;">Stop losing track of things</div>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.833rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); line-height: 1.6;">
            Tasks with due dates, priorities, and recurring schedules. Overdue items surface automatically. Attach checklists, documents, and notes so everything about a task lives in one place.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="v2-card" style="padding: 24px;">
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.03em; margin-bottom: 10px;">Goals</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.867rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-body); margin-bottom: 6px;">Turn "someday" into a plan</div>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.833rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); line-height: 1.6;">
            Set a counted target (run 100 miles) or break it into named steps (launch the website). A visual progress bar shows how far you've come. Increment with one tap.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="v2-card" style="padding: 24px;">
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.03em; margin-bottom: 10px;">Journal</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.867rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-body); margin-bottom: 6px;">Process your thoughts</div>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.833rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); line-height: 1.6;">
            A private journal with rich text, tagging, and search. Write freely or mark entries private so they don't preview in your list. Over time, your journal becomes a searchable record of how you've grown.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="v2-card" style="padding: 24px;">
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.03em; margin-bottom: 10px;">Daily Prep</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.867rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-body); margin-bottom: 6px;">Start each day with intention</div>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.833rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); line-height: 1.6;">
            Create your own daily reflection questions — "What's my top priority?" or "How am I feeling (1-10)?" — and answer them each morning. Review past answers to spot patterns in your mindset over weeks and months.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="v2-card" style="padding: 24px;">
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.03em; margin-bottom: 10px;">Notes & Documents</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.867rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-body); margin-bottom: 6px;">Keep your reference material close</div>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.833rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); line-height: 1.6;">
            Attach documents, YouTube videos, links, and files directly to habits. Your meditation habit can link to a guided audio. Your workout can reference a routine. Quick notes for everything else.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       DESIGN PHILOSOPHY
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 64px 0;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          Designed to disappear.
        </h2>
        <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--ink-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
          Most productivity apps compete for your attention with badges, points, and notifications. Habit Beaver does the opposite. It's a quiet tool that respects your focus.
        </p>
        <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--ink-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
          Check in, check off, move on. Your data is always there when you need it — in clean analytics, streak counts, and health scores — but it never shouts at you.
        </p>
        <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--ink-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
          Three themes. Your colors. Your categories. Your pace.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       HOW IT WORKS
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 64px 0;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 8px;">The compound effect is real.</h2>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.933rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 520px;">
        Small actions, repeated consistently, change everything. Here's how Habit Beaver makes consistency easy.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.733rem; color: var(--ink-faint); margin-bottom: 8px;">01</div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 6px;">Make it yours</div>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.867rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); line-height: 1.6;">
            Organize habits into categories that match your life. Set morning, afternoon, and evening blocks. Choose what matters most with custom priority levels. The system adapts to you, not the other way around.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.733rem; color: var(--ink-faint); margin-bottom: 8px;">02</div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 6px;">Two minutes a day</div>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.867rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); line-height: 1.6;">
            Open your dashboard, check off what you've done, and move on. The interface is fast and minimal on purpose — it shouldn't take longer to track a habit than to do it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.733rem; color: var(--ink-faint); margin-bottom: 8px;">03</div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 6px;">Watch yourself change</div>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.867rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); line-height: 1.6;">
            After a few weeks, your 90-day heatmap starts filling in. Streaks compound. Health scores climb. You stop wondering if you're making progress — you can see it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       ALSO INCLUDES
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 48px 0;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-8 gap-y-3" style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.833rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary);">
        <span><i class="fa-brands fa-google" style="margin-right: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem;"></i> Google Calendar sync</span>
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-moon" style="margin-right: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem;"></i> Dark mode</span>
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen" style="margin-right: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem;"></i> Mobile friendly</span>
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-list-check" style="margin-right: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem;"></i> Reusable checklists</span>
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-tags" style="margin-right: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem;"></i> Tags & search</span>
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-file-alt" style="margin-right: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem;"></i> File attachments</span>
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-repeat" style="margin-right: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem;"></i> Recurring tasks</span>
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse" style="margin-right: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem;"></i> Habit health scores</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       CTA
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 64px 0;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 12px;">
        Start today. It's free.
      </h2>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.933rem; color: var(--ink-tertiary); margin-bottom: 28px;">
        No credit card. No time limit. No catch.
      </p>
      <%= link_to new_user_registration_path, class: "v2-btn v2-btn-primary", style: "padding: 12px 28px; font-size: 0.933rem;" do %>
        Create your account
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<%= render 'shared/public_footer' %>
